### Health Check
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/health

### Create Wallet
POST {{base_url}}/api/v1/wallets
X-Api-Key: {{api_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "label": "My Primary Wallet"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("wallet_id", response.body.id);
%}

### List Wallets
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/wallets
X-Api-Key: {{api_key}}

### Get Address (ETH)
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/wallets/{{wallet_id}}/address/eth?index=0
X-Api-Key: {{api_key}}

### Get Address (TRON)
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/wallets/{{wallet_id}}/address/tron?index=0
X-Api-Key: {{api_key}}

### Get Address (SOL)
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/wallets/{{wallet_id}}/address/sol?index=0
X-Api-Key: {{api_key}}

### Sign Transaction
POST {{base_url}}/api/v1/wallets/{{wallet_id}}/sign
X-Api-Key: {{api_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "network": "eth",
  "index": 0,
  "unsigned_tx": "...hex..."
}
